request.doc:
Creating a group with group members:
POST https://{appliance_hostname}/mga/user_registry/groups/v1
POST_DATA: 
{
    "id":"OAuthPEGroup",
    "users": [
        "OAuthPEUser"
    ]
}

Creating a group without any group members:
POST https://{appliance_hostname}/mga/user_registry/groups/v1
POST_DATA: 
{
    "id":"OAuthPEGroup"
}
